title: Hour 3 - Troy Aikman
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Troy Aikman
description:
Dan Patrick breaks down how Tom Brady's divorce is impacting his play and how his "retirement" was a big pre-cursor to this all. Hall of Fame QB Troy Aikman joins to talk Tom Brady, Bears vs Cowboys, how he felt as a QB in run first offense, and more!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
